    <item>
      <title>中国维持基准贷款利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人民币贬值限制了北京的货币政策放松力度，中国连续第三个月维持基准贷款利率不变，正如预期的那样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，忠利集团投资委员会支持法国外贸银行资产管理交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/generalis-investment-committee-backs-natixis-asset-management-deal-sources-say-2025-01-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士周日表示，意大利保险公司忠利集团的投资委员会已经批准该集团与法国外贸银行投资管理公司 (Natixis Investment Managers) 达成的资产管理交易计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/generalis-investment-committee-backs-natixis-asset-management-deal-sources-say-2025-01-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 21:28:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，桑坦德银行在更广泛评估中审查英国零售银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/santander-considers-uk-exit-amid-frustrations-with-high-street-banking-ft-2025-01-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，桑坦德银行正在重新审视其在英国的业务。二十年前，桑坦德银行收购了 Abbey National，并成为英国商业街的主要参与者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/santander-considers-uk-exit-amid-frustrations-with-high-street-banking-ft-2025-01-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 09:19:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
